<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawiale Isu tawh bittak in chieh ka!
 Khawiale khawvela ei puihna chengah!
 Amah bei chun kipahna cheng tuoi ina,
 Khawiale Isu tawh bittak in chieh ka!

[V2]
 Khawiale! Khawiale!
 Lauhna nei puong ka;
 Khawiale Isu tawh bittak in chieh ka!

[V3]
 2. Khawiale Isu tawh kei ngawn ka hi puoi,
 Guolte'n ei nusieh mahleu Amah kei a;
 A khut chun lam lauhum ah eipui intin,
 Khawiale Isu tawh kipak in um kau.

[V4]
 3. Khawiale Isu tawh kipak in chieh kau,
 Thimna limin ei hun khuh ding lai inle!
 Hung halh ing ting, vakmang puong ka tih ka hei,
 Khawiale Isu umna mun nuom ahi.</lyrics>
<title>ANYWHERE WITH JESUS</title>
<hymn_number>161</hymn_number>
</song>